item.title: Linux Downtime – Episode 73
item.description: Amolith attempts to argue that avoiding ads using open source software is piracy, and that piracy in this case is good. See our contact page for ways to get in touch. Subscribe to the RSS feed. Feed: https://latenightlinux.com/feed/extra

item.title: Kerrang! Back Issues S03E24 No: 601 June 15 1996
item.description:
Issue no: 601. June 15 1996. This week we talk about Manic Street Preachers, Drain, Dog Eat Dog, Sugar Ray, Understand, The Prodigy, Rancid, Pennywise, Spacehog, Bon Jovi, Def Leppard, Compulsion, Downset, Prong, Three Fish, Bryan Adams, Madball, Angus OST, plus all of the regulars including feedback, lives, albums, news, and much more.
